    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Combine your <strong>pork & beef mince </strong>(remove the paper if required!) in a bowl with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up until thoroughly combined (clean hands is the best way!)</p><p>Divide and shape into 1 patty per person</p>",
