    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build your burger, spread some of the <strong>Irish-style tomato relish</strong> over a <strong>toasted brioche base</strong>, then top with<strong> </strong>a <strong>cheesy pork & beef patty</strong> and a <strong>toasted brioche lid </strong>– this is your<strong> Irish-style pork & beef burger</strong></p><p>Serve with the <strong>champ-inspired loaded fries</strong>, <strong>salad </strong>and <strong>remaining Irish-style tomato relish </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
